```
#### Please select the affected platforms
- [ ] Android
- [ ] iOS
- [ ] HTML/GWT
- [ ] Windows
- [ ] Linux
- [x] MacOS
#### Possible Fix:

It should be possible to directly set the cursor on the canvas using awt's tools.
